1. *Zlatni* prsten koji mi je poklonio muž je veoma dragocen. (The *golden* ring my husband gave me is very precious.)
2. Naš grad je poznat po *zlatnom* bokalu koji se dodeljuje pobednicima vinskog festivala. (Our city is known for the *golden* jug that is awarded to the winners of the wine festival.)
3. *Zlatna* ribica mi je omiljeni ljubimac još od detinjstva. (The *golden* fish has been my favorite pet since childhood.)
4. Završila sam knjigu o *zlatnom* dobu srpske književnosti. (I finished reading a book about the *golden* age of Serbian literature.)
5. *Zlatni* retriver je jedna od najpopularnijih rasa pasa na svetu. (The *golden* retriever is one of the most popular dog breeds in the world.)
6. *Zlatno* pravilo glasi da se drugima treba ponašati onako kako bismo želeli da se drugi ponašaju prema nama. (The *golden* rule is to treat others as you would like them to treat you.)
7. Naše olimpijske sportiste krasi *zlatna* medalja koju su osvojili na prethodnim igrama. (Our Olympic athletes are adorned with the *golden* medal they won at the previous games.)
8. *Zlatni* suncokreti u bašti su mi uvek bili omiljeni cvetovi. (The *golden* sunflowers in the garden have always been my favorite flowers.)
9. Sanjala sam o *zlatnom* priznanju za svoj rad u oblasti umetnosti. (I dreamed of a *golden* award for my work in the field of art.)
10. *Zlatni* saveti koje mi je dao deda su mi mnogo pomogli u životu. (The *golden* advice my grandfather gave me has helped me a lot in life.)